value.PublicRemarks:
Breathtaking 20 acre Extraordinary Equestrian Facility in Somis. This beautiful farm, currently operating as ''Whitethorne Ranch'' is nestled between Moorpark and Camarillo providing cool ocean breezes and a perfect atmosphere all year for both horses and riders. The boarding facilities include a total of 60 spacious stalls, made up of MD Barnmaster In & Out Stalls, MD Barnmaster Box Stalls, MD Barnmaster Foaling Stalls, each measuring 18'x24'. There are eight year-round large grass pastures including a hand grazing pasture, five standard pastures and ten large turnouts. Featuring two Grand Prix sized jumping arenas with permanent water jumps and liverpools and NEWCOURSE Jumps, an FEI standard sized dressage court with mirrors and Nike based footings by Footings Unlimited, a riding court, lunging arena and lighting for evening riding. There is also a walking trail and full quarter mile riding track surrounding a 3 acre grass field with Derby obstacles, 8 water jumps in addition to Grand Prix jumps, all adorned and edged with orange, grapefruit and pepper trees. The two jumping arenas have a special FIBAR footing mixture, which provides outstanding cushioning for your horses and reduces dust, all the while retaining moisture in the summer months and absorbing water in the rainy season. Your horses will also benefit from the 70 ft. diameter European Exerciser and 60 ft. Round Pen with a 7ft. wooden enclosure and double, full entry doors. A very unique new feature for the farm is the rehabilitation facility, dedicated to wellness and rejuvenation of equine athletes. The state of the art technology includes a covered Horse Gym USA Above Ground Equine Treadmill and a covered Vortex Wave Stimulation Equine Theraplate facility. Whether your horse requires some rest, post competition, or recovery from an injury, the onsite equipment can be tailored, with the guidance of your veterinarian, to meet your horses' needs. 

The property boasts two homes, providing over 11,000 square feet of living space combined. The main house is a 8,400 square foot custom built French Colonial Style, 4 bedrooms and 3 ½ bathrooms, a 3-car garage, covered patio area and several balconies all overlooking extensive stunning landscaping on 1.5 acres. The second home is approximately 2,000 square feet and has 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and a guest house with a double car port situated on a ½ acre but integrated into the ranch property. 

With easy access from State Route 23, State Route 118 and Interstate 101 freeways, the farm is nestled amongst citrus and avocado groves and offers a peaceful location away from the hustle and bustle and provides outstanding facilities for up to 100 horses.

value.PublicRemarks: This magnificent Mediterranean style estate sits on a beautiful equestrian 18 acre lot in a spectacular and private gated community of the Santa Monica mountains west to Paramount Ranch. Upon entering the home, a beautiful imperial staircase directs you to a mesmerizing view of the private grounds with a fabulous pool and spa. At over 13,000 square feet, this property is an entertainer's dream. The grand kitchen features two full sized islands, and a breakfast nook that is complemented by natural light from the floor to ceiling windows. Complete with exposed beam ceilings that opens up to a seating area with a gorgeous stone fireplace and skylight windows. Connected to the spacious seating area is a private dining room that opens up to the outdoor patio which is great for entertaining. The formal living room includes arched windows, a beautiful limestone fireplace, and two doors opening to the patio area as well. The classic wood-paneled library offers a cozy sanctuary complete with nature views that can be appreciated through the arched windows. The impressive estate features two primary suites included both upstairs and downstairs, three guest bedrooms, and a gym. The expansive gym has mirrors installed throughout and an en-suite sauna. The gym opens up to the balcony which displays mountain views for a zen feeling and an immediate sense of calm, peace, and quiet. Secluded in its own wilderness playground, this property boasts a bocce ball court, two putting greens, and a gorgeous tennis court. Ideally situated only 5 minutes from the 101 freeway, Paramount Ranch is only a short drive to both the beach and the city. This unique property magically envelops you in your own personal paradise.

value.PublicRemarks:
Welcome to your own secluded gated paradise nestled on a hilltop in the prestigious North Ranch Country Club Estates. This recently reimagined single story estate is located on one of the most sought after streets in the community and boasts views of the surrounding foothills.

Exceptionally remodeled, tastefully blending its traditional features with a modern aesthetic, this estate has been expertly designed to meet the highest standards of contemporary living. As you step inside, you will be struck by the perfect combination of warm neutral tones, soaring ceilings and light filled windows, magnificent light fixtures and modern finishes that create a sleek and sophisticated atmosphere.

The estate features a main house with 5 bedrooms and 7 baths and a separate studio guest suite with kitchenette and full bathroom. The open concept gourmet kitchen features Wolf stainless steel appliances, subzero refrigerator and ample storage in the spacious butler's pantry. Entertain and gather with ease around the generously sized quartz center island with waterfall finish. The floor-to-ceiling windows allow natural light to flood the space, while the soaring ceilings create an airy and spacious feel. Adjacent you'll find a great room with wood beam ceilings and stunning stone fireplace. Additional features include your stunning home theater with new leather reclining seats, wine/bar room with custom lighting, quartz countertops and bar top seating, stunning library finished with floor to ceiling built-ins and coffered ceiling, and two laundry rooms.

The primary suite is abundant with natural light and offers a generous seating area and French door sliders to your private patio. The magnificent en suite bath boasts dual vanities, large soaking tub with garden views and luxurious dual zone shower. Dual walk-in closets complete the lavish retreat.

The professionally landscaped grounds of this estate are truly a rare offering with an abundance of space for entertaining and recreation. Rolling green lawns, lush gardens, custom pool and spa and sizable patios and gazebo allow you unlimited opportunities to enjoy this private sanctuary.

The estate features a circular driveway and separate gated motor court with ample parking for multiple cars and a four-car garage.

Experience luxury living at its finest with this guard gated North Ranch Country Club estate. Don't miss this opportunity to own a piece of paradise in one of the most exclusive communities in Westlake Village.

Ideal location in the heart of Westlake Village, offering a variety of fine & casual dining, shopping, top rated schools and an easy drive to beautiful California beaches.

value.PublicRemarks:
Welcome to an unparalleled residence of opulence, refinement, and architectural mastery in this exclusive Tuscan Villa nestled within the gated sanctuary of 'The Oaks of Calabasas'! Poised on nearly an acre of lush, private grounds, this extraordinary estate embodies the pinnacle of luxury living and provides the uniquely private location you've been looking for, with virtually no neighbors behind or beside the residence!
As you approach the grand entrance, a majestic circular driveway with a fountain unveils itself, setting the stage for this magnificent 5-bedroom, 6.5-bathroom residence spanning approximately 6,756 square feet of sublime living space. Step into the awe-inspiring foyer, graced by a dazzling chandelier and soaring ceilings, which effortlessly imparts a sense of unparalleled grandeur and expanse.
Proceed to the formal living room, where a stately fireplace and expansive floor-to ceiling windows reveal a secluded atrium with a tranquil fire pit, or ascend to the remarkable library, adorned with intricately carved custom built-ins, artisanal finishes, and dramatic high ceilings that evoke an aura of sophistication and intellect.
One of two regal staircases leads from the library to the upper level. On the lower level, discover a sumptuous bedroom with an en-suite bathroom and a discreet private entrance, perfectly poised for guests or intimate retreats.
The grand formal dining room, designed for extravagant gatherings, boasts a wine closet capable of accommodating hundreds of your most cherished bottles. A beautiful fountain just outside the dining room windows is a lovely focal point.  Just steps away, a butler's pantry equipped for executive-level entertainment, includes a  Sub Zero, temperature-controlled wine cooler and refrigerator.
Prepare to be mesmerized by the gourmet kitchen, a masterpiece adorned with Viking, Thermador and Sub-Zero appliances and featuring a large center island and eating area with picturesque mountain and backyard vistas. 
 Adjacent to the kitchen, a cozy family room with a fireplace welcomes you to relax and admire the serene views of the backyard and the inviting pool area.
A second staircase ascends from this area to the upper level, where the secluded primary suite awaits. Revel in the opulence of a sitting area, complemented by a fireplace and balcony/patio offering vistas of the pool, backyard, and a breathtaking panorama of rolling hills, valleys, and city lights or stroll to your primary suite bathroom and soak in your private tub with lovely backyard and mountain views! This home leaves no desire unfulfilled.
Just off the primary suite entrance, a refined billiards area boasts panoramic views, and a royal junior suite, exuding privacy, is discreetly nestled away from the other bedrooms. Two additional en-suite bedrooms on the upper level provide every comfort and amenity one could desire.
The backyard is an absolute masterpiece, featuring meticulously landscaped gardens, multiple fire pits, an expansive barbecue area, putting green, sports court, and an impressive, resort-style pool and spa adorned with captivating water features and treatments. An outdoor fireplace and a dramatic cabana with a full bath, overlook the splendid pool area and lush backyard, creating a haven of relaxation and entertainment.
The gated motor court and attached garage are a car enthusiast's dream, offering ample space for multiple vehicles and recreational toys. Adjacent to the motor court, a private gym/office provides an oasis for staying committed to your fitness and well-being.
From the Mar Siena travertine to the state-of-the-art surround sound system, custom lighting, and elegant granite accents, this estate is tailored for the discerning buyer in search of a residence that stands alone in its uniqueness and allure. Come and embrace the extraordinary, and savor every facet of life within the prestigious enclave at 'The Oaks of Calabasas.'

value.PublicRemarks: Welcome to Malibu Mountain Estates! A one of a kind trophy masterpiece boasting jaw dropping jet liner views unmatched in Southern California! A brand new European Contemporary designed by the award winning firm of GoDesign21. Custom built using only the finest finishes, the over 6500 square foot showplace provides complete privacy in the Santa Monica mountains. Ideally set in a small gated community in the much desired Malibou Lake area, the home sits up a 400 foot private driveway atop 3.41 acres. Enter through the 9'x5' swivel glass pivot door to an epic open concept floorplan and dramatic walls of glass to take advantage of the panoramic views! Interior features include multiple sets of sliding doors, soaring two story ceilings, temp controlled wine wall, screening room and much more. The true chefs kitchen spares no expense with Leicht German Cabinetry, quartz counters and top of the line appliances, The spa quality primary suite is graced with two large walk in closets, fireplace, glass enclosed wrap around balcony, and a Four Seasons dream bathroom. Other interior features include 4 additional en-suite bedrooms and a very special indoor/outdoor covered gym and massage area. The grounds are second to none creating an ambiance that is impossible to find anywhere else. There is an infinity edge pool and spa, lower level outdoor kitchen, drought tolerant landscape and breathtaking views from everywhere! Other amenities include an AMAZING 1700 square foot roof top deck with tv, outdoor speakers and 360 degree views! Additionally the estate provides smart home technology, 13 security cameras, invisible door hinges, flushed baseboards with shadow lines, 5 zoned HVAC, solar system, audio speakers throughout, 10 inch white Oak floors from Spain and too much more to mention. This must been seen in person to appreciate! A very special offering with close proximity to the 101, shopping, restaurants, Malibu and the Conejo and San Fernando Valleys.

Extraordinary Equestrian Estate Property! Set on 20 serene acres in Moorpark, this private farm, currently known as H&H Farms, is the ultimate combination of recreation and tranquility with breathtaking views of the mountains, valley and grounds. Two state-of-the art breezeway barns with 30 European bamboo lumber stalls, a showcase arena with all-weather GGT footing, multiple covered and uncovered pastures, a European hot walker and various sized turnouts all provide your horses with every equestrian amenity. Barn includes oversized stalls, tack room, cross-tie and wash rack areas,  full laundry and feed room and expansive clubhouse. Serving as the home to top competitive riders and amateur enthusiasts in several riding and showing disciplines, this farm has been designed with your horse in mind. You and your horses will enjoy trail access to riding trails, 360 degree views and incredible natural beauty all within the prestigious Moorpark riding community. 

The site includes (1) 1,200 square foot manufactured home suitable for manager or caretaker living quarters with (4) bedrooms & (2) bathrooms with a detached garage. 
The property is one parcel but is in the process of being split into (2) 10-acre parcels with the unique opportunity to build. This is an incredible value add that will allow you to build up to (2) custom estate homes, overlooking your farm and the entire valley... all the way to the ocean on a clear day!

The spectacular natural beauty of this property also provides exceptional privacy with only (1) common property line, many mature trees and beautiful landscaping. 

And all within close proximity of the 23 & 118 freeways with very easy access to shops and restaurants.

Entertainer's Paradise, Overlooking Lake Sherwood! This is a special opportunity to own a spectacularly updated and upgraded home in the privately guard-gated community of Lake Sherwood with breathtakingly beautiful panoramic lake views and your own private boat dock. The home is currently under construction and will be completed in late 2023, but the renderings and plans are included in the listing documents and photos to show the finished product. Purchase includes the finished home with existing plans and current design. As you will see, this home will be 5,513 square feet of rebuilt living space with a brand new open floor plan, expansive entertaining spaces on both levels, tons of natural light, luxurious finishes, a chef's kitchen and custom finishes throughout. The architect and designers have created a truly astonishing Contemporary Spanish home with special touches and intricate details, all available to modify and upgrade once this home becomes yours. There are now 5 bedrooms, several with lake views and 2 with patios and decks attached, and 5 bathrooms throughout. 

The Lake Sherwood lifestyle allows you to enjoy boating, kayaking, paddle boarding, fishing and so much more. In addition to water activities, residents in the Lake Sherwood Community may apply for membership at any of the three exclusive private clubs. These clubs offer outstanding amenities including 2 Jack Nicklaus designed golf courses, tennis courts, pickleball courts, spa amenities and swimming pools. Located just 9 miles from Malibu and minutes away from world class restaurants and high end shopping, this is your opportunity to live in one of Southern California's most desirable guard-gated communities.
